Business Acquisitions. Our investments in businesses net of cash acquired in 2020, 2019 and 2018 totaled $35,077 million
(including debt assumed of $4,700 million and stock issued of $33,166 million), $9 million, and $30,783 million (including debt
assumed of $7,784 million and stock issued of $7,960 million) respectively. Our investments in businesses in 2020 and 2018
primarily consisted of the acquisition of Raytheon Company and Rockwell Collins, Inc. (Rockwell Collins), respectively.
