million, $27 million and $36 million, respectively, with an associated tax benefit realized of $48 million, $75 million and $59
million, respectively. In addition, for the years ended December 31, 2020, 2019 and 2018, the associated tax benefit realized from
the vesting of performance share units, restricted stock awards and RSUs was $58 million, $36 million and $13 million,
respectively.
